{"tid":207961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉繼歡係内地尊才，17歲偷渡黎香港","createTime":"2017-04-19T08:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T15:15:30.000Z","uid":71949,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"906f22fe8b8317863026757369c77df01d89a3a7","tid":207961,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔係血統至上架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次支那國有人死都會拍手叫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔理人地無唔無辜，慘唔慘<br />\n呢個葉生係17嵗偷渡黎香港既支那仔，<br />\n打家劫社，殺死香港途人，仲衰過腥香港人。<br />\n<br />\n雖然警犬係仆街，但唔好非黑即白得咁On9好冇?唔好咁痴線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b789ca27c9a5bcaadce4e9263105cdaa5785e1","tid":207961,"uid":102056,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:38:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c9ea5049707f67a2e94565e44271465b21a6ae6","tid":207961,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:41:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登仔唔係血統至上架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次支那國有人死都會拍手叫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔理人地無唔無辜，慘唔慘<br />\n呢個葉生係17嵗偷渡黎香港既支那仔，<br />\n打家劫社，殺死香港途人，仲衰過腥香港人。<br />\n<br />\n雖然警犬係仆街，但唔好非黑即白得咁On9好冇?唔好咁痴線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔通推d濕鳩大學雞玩賓周當有趣果d上神枱咩<br />\n<br />\n歡哥係做實事既人，識英雄仲英雄，大劉都有份出錢幫葉繼歡屋企人，你就知咩叫做識英雄仲英雄<br />\n<br />\n東漢未年，劉關張也是無讀過書既市井之徒，也可以流芳百世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲你老母咩字都唔識多隻 唔怪得叫呢d人做英雄啦"},{"pid":"596a7f6f3c4105cdb6a2c11e8c9ed07b61e8d6dc","tid":207961,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登仔唔係血統至上架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次支那國有人死都會拍手叫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.g